{
  "stem": "18670.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So these were some of the jobs I had in between.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes I was gone for a week, for 10 days, sometimes two weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I came back to my outfit again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And finally we got in-- after Bastogne and all the things, different things happened, finally we got into Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we've made it to Mainz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Mainz, we became the military government of Mainz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We took over whole area, one of the suburbs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mainz was bombed for 22 minutes and completely destroyed, completely.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the suburbs of Mainz were still all right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we cleaned out the whole area of Mainz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had a commanding officer who was of German background.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I experienced some anti-Semitism in American Army too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Originally when I was a mess sergeant, there was a mess sergeant in another mess hall, the other-- there were two mess halls, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had a habit that I never followed the menu that was given to us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- special, as a matter of fact, mess halls were rated-- and again, not to brag, but I'm bragging about it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mess hall was the number one in the whole division.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They finally issued tickets, because everybody was coming to the mess hall, eating in our place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this mess sergeant came in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was upset because I didn't follow the menu and he did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we got the reputation having such a wonderful mess hall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he started to get ornery.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then one [INAUDIBLE] said to another one, he says, if you didn't have those stripes, he says, you Jew bastard, he says, I'll beat the heck out of you.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For a minute I felt like to take my jacket off.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
